  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Researchers are trying to incorporate a process known as Functional MRI (fMRI) scanning to
      reveal a pattern in brain activity during Deep Brain Stimulation (DBS), which will correlate
      to possible seizure freedom.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
